    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IMPORTANT NOTE:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THIS DEMO WAS AN ALPHA PREVIEW OF COMBAT AND EXPLORATION. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The full game is much more polished, performant, balanced, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, grapple, double jump, and surf your way through the sprawling open world of Echo Point. Search every corner of the world for powerful weapons and character upgrades. Mow down squads of ruthless mercenaries. Climb and take down giant colossi bosses as large as skyscrapers. Follow the main quest or explore at your own pace in both single player and 4 player co-op.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic first person combat with satisfying weapons and loads of movement options.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/cd23d645be297043ea607cb1e702fea3.poster.avif?t=1727028410\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/cd23d645be297043ea607cb1e702fea3.webm?t=1727028410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/cd23d645be297043ea607cb1e702fea3.mp4?t=1727028410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the open world of Echo Point. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/02c8fb8ab7a9602d61c662047eb47aa2.poster.avif?t=1727028410\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/02c8fb8ab7a9602d61c662047eb47aa2.webm?t=1727028410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/02c8fb8ab7a9602d61c662047eb47aa2.mp4?t=1727028410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up and gain new abilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/9c1bdbe21fc9220c20e390878b3f23af.poster.avif?t=1727028410\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/9c1bdbe21fc9220c20e390878b3f23af.webm?t=1727028410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/9c1bdbe21fc9220c20e390878b3f23af.mp4?t=1727028410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join your friends in four player coop!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/6e0d47ba014b2c1d48bbca2d5cf01517.poster.avif?t=1727028410\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/6e0d47ba014b2c1d48bbca2d5cf01517.webm?t=1727028410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398180/extras/6e0d47ba014b2c1d48bbca2d5cf01517.mp4?t=1727028410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
